column5: Shortly after getting my line in the water, I thought I had hooked a decent walleye, the muskie stayed down and just dogged it for a minute or so with the colder water     we did pretty good on the target species later, nice night with the full moon
That beats sitting on yer arse at home.  A nice surprise fish.
Good job! Anytime out on the water is great! Thanks for the report.
Yum yum! nice size walleye right there. From shore too looking at the photo.
Nice catch Chris !!!! Wow!!! Another walleye dinner ... Cheers man !!!! Tight-lines
